Usage: get_ports [-help] [-filter <expr>] [-nocase] [-quiet] [-regexp] [ <patterns> | -of_objects <object_list> ]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<patterns>                    # Patterns for port names (string, optional)
-filter <expr>                # Filters the collection with the specified
                              # expression (string, optional)
-nocase                       # Pattern matching is not case sensitive
                              # (bool, optional)
-of_objects <object_list>     # Creates a collection of all ports associated
                              # with the specified nets (string, optional)
-quiet                        # Suppresses all error and warning messages
                              # generated when the get_ports command is run
                              # (bool, optional)
-regexp                       # Suppresses all error and warning messages
                              # generated when the get_ports command is run
                              # (bool, optional)